Title: 14.2 Loadable Function Reference
Name: firewall_group_delist()
Description:
This function removes an account from a group profile. It
              requires the FIREWALL_ADMIN
              privilege.
Press CTRL+C to copy SELECT firewall_group_delist('g', 'fwuser@localhost');
This function was added in MySQL 8.0.23.
